<h5>Results</h5>
<p>From the results of my desktop research and interviews with local community members and business owners, I was able to identify the commonly used online platforms used by both to search and promote online businesses. These included social media pages, online business directories, business websites and local community webpages.</p>
<p>The interviews provided valuable information on the benefits and drawbacks of these platforms from the audiences perspectives. To to help make sense of my interview findings, I grouped common findings through the tool of an affinity map. </p>   
